---
---
<section class="section projects-section" id="projects">
    <div class="section-container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <span class="section-tag frosted-glass">
                <span class="section-tag-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="12" height="12" fill="currentColor">
                        <path d="M12 2L14.85 9.15L22 12L14.85 14.85L12 22L9.15 9.15L12 2Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                </span>
                ผลงาน
            </span>
            <h2 class="section-title">My Creations</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="projects-grid">

            <!-- Sora-Novel Card -->
            <div class="project-card frosted-glass">
                <div class="project-info">
                    <div class="project-meta">
                        <span class="project-category">
                            <span class="project-cat-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path>
                                    <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <span>AI VISUAL NOVEL / INTERACTIVE GAME</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="project-status-badge beta">AI MEMORY SYSTEM</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="project-name">Sora-Novel</h3>
                    <p class="project-desc">
                        Visual Novel แบบ Dynamic Branch ที่มาพร้อมกับระบบ AI Memory ช่วยจดจำพฤติกรรมและการตัดสินใจของผู้เล่นเพื่อปรับเปลี่ยนบทสนทนา (แต่เนื้อเรื่องทั้งหมดเขียนโดยมนุษย์ ไม่ใช่ AI นะจ๊ะ)
                    </p>
                    <div class="project-tech-tags">
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Gemini 3.5 Flash</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">AI Memory System</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Dynamic Storytelling</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Vanilla JS</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">CSS Grid / Flexbox</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-buttons">
                        <a href="https://sora-novel.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary project-btn">
                            <span>เข้าชมเว็บไซต์</span>
                            <span class="btn-arrow">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
                                    <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/celestial-sora/Sora-Novel" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-outline project-btn">
                            <span>ดูโค้ดบน GitHub</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- GitHub Profile Card -->
            <div class="project-card frosted-glass">
                <div class="project-info">
                    <div class="project-meta">
                        <span class="project-category">
                            <span class="project-cat-icon">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <path d="M16 18l6-6-6-6M8 6l-6 6 6 6"></path>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                            <span>GitHub Profile / Repositories</span>
                        </span>
                        <span class="project-status-badge beta">Active</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="project-name">celestial-sora</h3>
                    <p class="project-desc">
                        คลังเก็บรวบรวมซอร์สโค้ด โปรเจกต์พัฒนาซอฟต์แวร์ และการ Rice ระบบปฏิบัติการ Linux ของฉัน บน GitHub สามารถเข้ามาดูและร่วมพัฒนาโปรเจกต์ต่างๆ ได้เลย!
                    </p>
                    <div class="project-tech-tags">
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Git Repositories</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Open Source</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Linux Rice</span>
                        <span class="tech-tag frosted-glass">Vibe Coding</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="project-buttons">
                        <a href="https://github.com/celestial-sora" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-primary project-btn">
                            <span>ดูบน GitHub</span>
                            <span class="btn-arrow">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="14" height="14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                                    <line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"></line>
                                    <polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
                                </svg>
                            </span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>
